Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:41.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gathering shards of the Sacred Jewel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:45.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we continue our journey to\nbattle our arch-enemy Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is so dense,\nhe hasn't noticed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:53.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it seems that Miroku the monk\nand Sango the Demon Slayer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}have feelings for each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:00.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, they're both hesitant\nabout declaring their feelings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the relationship hasn't\nprogressed at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:22.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:23.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:27.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:36.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:06.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But my young lord,\nwhat about the other personage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave no stone unturned!\NFind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should use an umbrella, too,\NInuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only kids and women use\nthat stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cling to pride and\nyou'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'm not such a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umbrellas are useful for\na number of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:51.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't feel a demonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:03:59.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:00.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... and a lot of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:17.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Sango the Demon Slayer\nand her travel party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:18.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, we are they.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Takeda Clan vassal\NMiwanosuke Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have come to speak\nto Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to request that you\ndestroy a demon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that has plagued our castle\nnight after night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:40.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will not question\nyour methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Minor damages to the castle\nwill be tolerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here is an advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After the beast is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you will receive an amount\nequal to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is not a bad offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ten times... Twenty times\nwhat is normally charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you'll agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The terms are too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You cannot refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:17.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem to have totally forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I don't blame her\nfor not remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we mustn't talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a fine castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pardon the late introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Kuranosuke Takeda,\nlord of this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A clan lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder he acts pompous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kuranosuke Takeda...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, that time...\nthe runny-nosed kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I mean... Young lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it was six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:22.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My castle had been plagued\nby a demon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and we had hired your group\nto slay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a magnificent sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like a single lily in the\nbloody battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were so awe-inspiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awe-inspiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, let me come to the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango! Destroy the beast,\nthen marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! This is so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had decided the moment\NI saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who will become\nmy wife... is you, Sango, and only you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you will accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:15.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Men! Prepare rooms\nfor the guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:16.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:24.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:34.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango is a candidate\nto become a lord's bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:38.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What'll I do?\NHow do I refuse?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:46.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Surely you jest, Master Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no.\NIt's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That man is so maddening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:22.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Goodness! There was no need\nto slap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't have to flirt with\na girl like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango was so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:35.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku flirts all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:40.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't understand a thing,\NInuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:44.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango wants Miroku to\nstop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is so dense!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this may be\njust the chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku has to be\nconcerned about Sango.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So if I just give him\na little push...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And now that's decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh! Kagome,\nwhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Must you ask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you realize Sango\nmight get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:55.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... It's something\NSango must decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's none of our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, any woman would\ndo for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You... without fortune, home,\nor status...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just a flirtatious, itinerant monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On the other hand, a clan lord who\nis young, handsome and rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Earnest and focused and\nunlikely to stray...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's a huge catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess there's absolutely\nno question who's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What? Well?\NAre you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to check something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:45.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it... You are concerned,\nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Miroku!\NWhy can't you come clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, your sudden appearance\nis what scared me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:37.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What'll I do?\NI don't want to hurt him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can I show her\nhow I feel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:54.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:58.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't call me "lord."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just call me Kuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can even call me\NRunny-Nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:05.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just jesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know the kind of\nworld we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are few I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil demons abound in\nmountains and rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:22.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And mortals resort to trickery\nand betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We call this the world\nabove hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I am not satisfied with\nhow things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:32.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I swore that at least the woman\NI spend my life with
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,will be someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you choose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I AM the lord of a clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know I am a good judge\nof people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:12:59.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you will marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is something\NI must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:21.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will probably be very\ndifficult to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:27.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:32.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must do this or I cannot\ngo forward in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I must\ncontinue my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please! You must find\nsomeone more suitable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have waited six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It matters not how many more\nyears I must wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, I understand how\nyou feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... no... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you are ever in trouble,\ncome to me without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:04.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will do everything\nin my power to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why let her go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:23.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I'm truly concerned about\NSango's happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it's best that I let\nher be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:29.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her fate was shattered\nby the evil Naraku
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and she continues to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now she has a chance to\nmarry Lord Takeda and settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which will bring her happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no need to even think\nabout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you will\nunderstand someday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what about Sango's feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:15.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:49.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So he's come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:04.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, it'll all be over\nwith a swing of my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do it!\NYou stay out of this, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can handle this small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides... I'm in a real bad mood,\nright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:23.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you say something to her,\NMiroku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? No... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:17:00.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen Sango\nlooking so fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:05.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... No one in this world\ncould take her on at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come crying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:11.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:17.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the finishing blow...\NHiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You did it, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You miscalculated, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I realized it after watching\nyou fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This demon is actually\na vengeful spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:06.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It cannot be destroyed\nthe usual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil spirit exorcism!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bear ornaments?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then these bears' vengeful spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:58.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A bear pelt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:04.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the demon we exterminated\nsix years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we instructed the clan\nto offer prayers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then bury it in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were following your\ninstructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and were about to bury it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when we were stopped\nby the late lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:24.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Instead, in accordance\nwith his orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,wood carvings were made and\ndesignated clan treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to use as a way to restore\nthe clan's finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furthermore, big-bear bean jam cakes,\nbig-bear towels and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,big-bear coins were marketed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But they didn't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kuranosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind. Say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand well\nhow you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go. Your friends await.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:32.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango, I haven't given up yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, what happened\nto that hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, the strap broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is your wound okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:14.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um... Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:22.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That we can continue\nour journey together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you smiling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:32.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to that umbrella, those two\nlook pretty happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:50.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Inuyasha.\NDo you know {\i1}janken?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:52.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who's always\nsticking around Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Jaken. I meant\nrock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.35,0:23:57.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here we go,\njan, ken, scissors! ...I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Strange things're happening today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:02.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rock-paper-scissors!\NI win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:04.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that Jaken?\NIs he after the Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Jaken's Plan to Steal the Tetsusaiga"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:13.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never Jaken...\njust rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:14.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
